          <br />
          <h4>About CRL (GAD)</h4>
          <p>
            The lush green campus of Central Research Laboratory, Ghaziabad
            (CRL-GAD) is located in Ghaziabad, Uttar Pradesh. It has been
            established with the following objectives:
          </p>
          <ul>
            <li>
              To generate new ideas and concepts that can result in new or
              improved products.
            </li>
            <li>
              Examine emerging concepts and technologies and adapt them for new
              products and systems.
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="vision-container" id="vision-section">
          <h2><i>Our Vision</i></h2>
          <p>
            Our vision is to empower teams to achieve their highest potential
            through efficient project management tools that streamline
            processes, foster collaboration, and drive innovation.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
